      "text": "And this one is that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was always telling me stories about the people whom he saved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he was entertained every single year by the Israeli government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was invited to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they used to throw a banquet for him and entertain him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he was a big hero in Israel, and rightly so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was the only one who really saved 1,100 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
